ACTION TAKEN:

A check of the suspect IP address resolved to Comcast with a geo-location of Elkton, MD.  A check of the potential child victim's IP address also resolved to Comcast with a geo-location of Pasadena, MD.  Cpl. Heid authored a subpoena to the Anne Arundel County State's Attorneys Office for Comcast and will be awaiting its return.  The case will remain open at this time.
